These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pomegranate
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, coffee
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
3. the person drinking 7up is the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | pomegranate | cauliflower | pineapple |
| Beverage    | iced-tea    | coffee | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, chef, police-officer
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the chef is in an even position##4
3. the police-officer is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the chef is the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | drawing | filmmaking | board-games |
| Job   | police-officer    | chef     | nurse        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, architect, videographer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the accountant is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the architect is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Job         | videographer     | architect | accountant |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, superhero
City: paris, hannover, liverpool
1. the person watching sports movies is the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | sports  | musical  |
| City         | paris  | hannover | liverpool |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, folk, rock
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is camping and the fan of gospel##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | camping   | gardening | chess    |
| Music-Genre   | folk | rock     | gospel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, backgammon
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person playing scrabble is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing canasta is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Game   | canasta | backgammon | scrabble   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, martial-arts
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, canasta
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is between the person playing canasta and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | horror |
| Game           | domino         | mah-jongg         | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, carrot, kale
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, grey, turquise
1. the person who likes light-blue is between the person who likes grey and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the person who likes turquise is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | kale | artichoke |
| Color    | grey    | light-blue | turquise     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, funk
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, project-manager, doctor
1. the doctor is in an odd position##4
2. the project-manager is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the doctor is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the doctor is on the left or right of the project-manager##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | dubstep  | ambient  |
| Job         | doctor | project-manager | electrician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
House: tower, townhouse, craftsman
There 3 different types of food: corn, garlic, pineapple
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the craftsman house##1
2. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| House   | tower    | craftsman      | townhouse |
| Food       | garlic | pineapple | corn   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, poker
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, trike
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the person playing bridge##1
3. the person driving the trike is the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing poker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Game         | whist | poker | bridge |
| Transport   | subway | trike   | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, colombian, nigerian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, june, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the australian is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the colombian##3
4. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | colombian | australian |
| Birthday     | june     | october   | february        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, mechanic, accountant
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the accountant##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the mechanic##1
3. the accountant is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Job   | accountant  | coach | mechanic   |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | cycling |

