.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, pop, disco
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the fan of disco is between the fan of pop and the owner of the pony##2
2. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of disco is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | pop | disco | trance |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
