The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
4. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | october  | november     | january |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

