.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, march, december
3 different pets are kept: hamster, pony, turtle
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | october | december | march    |
| Pet           | pony     | turtle  | hamster |

