.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, gardening, hiking
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, bellflower, tulip
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | hiking | camping   | gardening |
| Flower   | bellflower   | azalea | tulip      |

